Replaces: sugar-activity-turtlebots, sugar-default-activities
Description: TurtleBlocks with robotic plugins
 TurtleBots is a modified version of TurtleBlocks, it includes several plugins 
 to manage robotic kits such as Butia, Sumbot, Lego NXT, Lego WeDo, Arduino
 boards, and FischerTechnik ROBO LT.
 Also includes two plugins for vision: FollowMe and Pattern detection.
 If you have another robotic kit feel free to make a new plugin, and if you
 want you can send us the code so we can add your plugin to TurtleBots! :-)
 TurtleBots is part of "Proyecto Butiá" - "Sistema robótico constructivo
 programable de bajo costo para uso educativo" (Programmable, constructive and 
 low cost robotic kit for educational purpose)
